metadata.name: DOUBLE SOUL
metadata.description:
"Double Soul" is my work in B&W that I appreciate the most.

An analog photograph taken, developed and scanned by me.
It is my most artisanal work taken to the digital world.
Fast forwarding into decades of photography evolution.

A soul unfolding to reach the unattainable.

1/1 piece

Camera: Nikon FM II
Lens: Nikon 50mm 1.8
Film: ILFORD HP5 plus 400



2872 × 4270 px   ||  6.7mb  ||  .jpg

Collector can claim a signed A5 physical foam print.

Minted in January 2022 by @Sr_Zeta.

Carlos Marín.
